meta {
  name: Get presigned url document-management
  type: http
  seq: 4
}

get {
  url: {{host}}/api/{{bu_code}}/documents/:filetoken/presigned-url
  body: none
  auth: bearer
}

headers {
  x-app-id: {{x_app_id}}
}

auth:bearer {
  token: {{access_token}}
}

query {
  ~expirySeconds:
}

params:path {
  filetoken: {{filetoken}}
}

docs {
  ## Get Presigned URL
  สร้าง presigned URL สำหรับเข้าถึงเอกสารอย่างปลอดภัย

  Generates a time-limited presigned URL for secure, direct access to a procurement document, enabling browser-based viewing or sharing without exposing permanent storage credentials.

  ### Path Parameters
  | Name | Type | Description |
  |------|------|-------------|
  | `bu_code` | string | Business unit code |
  | `filetoken` | string | Unique file token returned from upload |

  ### Query Parameters
  | Name | Type | Required | Default | Description |
  |------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
  | `expirySeconds` | number | No | 3600 | URL expiry duration in seconds |

  ### Headers
  | Name | Required | Description |
  |------|----------|-------------|
  | `Authorization` | Yes | `Bearer {{access_token}}` |
  | `x-app-id` | Yes | `{{x_app_id}}` |

  ### Permissions
  > Permission key not found in seed; review needed.

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "url": "https://storage.example.com/files/vendor-invoice-2026-04.pdf?X-Amz-Signature=abc123&X-Amz-Expires=3600"
    },
    "paginate": null,
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
  }
  ```

  ### Error Responses
  | Status | When |
  |--------|------|
  | 401 | Missing or invalid Bearer token |
  | 404 | File token not found in storage |
}
